premise_source_doc_sentence: The Complete Works of William Shakespeare  (  Abridged  )   (  also known as The Compleat Wrks of Wllm Shkspr  (  Abridged  )   )  is a play written by Adam Long , Daniel Singer , and Jess Winfield that parodies the plays of William Shakespeare with all of them being performed  (  in comically shortened or merged form  )  by only three actors .
(  The Soldier 's Tale  )  is a theatrical work `` to be read , played , and danced '' by three actors and one or several dancers , accompanied by a septet of instruments .
Only three actors from the two previous films appear in this third one , Christian Clavier , Jean Reno and Marie-Anne Chazel .
The three actors play their musical instruments and speak with mock English accents throughout the movie .

The music is scored for a septet of violin , double bass , clarinet , bassoon , cornet  (  often played on trumpet  )  , trombone , and percussion , and the story is told by three actors : the soldier , the devil , and a narrator , who also takes on the roles of minor characters .
